opular pickup and dropoff locations among passengers.\n\n2. **Problem 2: Analyzing Trip Patterns by Vendor**\n   Explore variations in trip patterns based on different taxi vendors.\n\n3. **Problem 3: Understanding Payment Preferences**\n   Analyze payment preferences and identify trends in payment behavior among passengers.","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"<h2 style=\"background:black; border:0; color:#FFFF00; padding: 20px; text-align: center\">\n    IMPORTING PACKAGES\n</h2>","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"library(dplyr)\nlibrary(tidyr)\nlibrary(stats)","metadata":{"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2023-08-22T16:43:29.248548Z","iopub.execute_input":"2023-08-22T16:43:29.250536Z","iopub.status.idle":"2023-08-22T16:43:29.269832Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":27,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"<h2 style=\"background:black; border:0; color:#FFFF00; padding: 20px; text-align: center\">\n    LOADING DATASET\n</h2>","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"**For starters let's import Dataset first**\n\n> **read.csv2() function is used to import/read dataset**","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"Taxi <- read.csv2('/kaggle/input/taxi-trip-data-nyc/taxi_tripdata.csv',sep=',')","metadata":{"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2023-08-22T15:49:03.929636Z","iopub.execute_input":"2023-08-22T15:49:03.931315Z","iopub.status.idle":"2023-08-22T15:49:04.493459Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":5,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"<h2 style=\"background:black; border:0; color:#FFFF00; padding: 20px; text-align: center\">\n    EXPLORING DATASET \n</h2>","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"## **HERE WE'LL BE SIMPLY EXPLORING DATASET BY LEARNING IT'S STRUCTURE, SHAPE ETC**","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"> **nrow() and ncol(): Get the number of rows and columns in the dataset.**","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"rows <- nrow(Taxi)\ncols <- ncol(Taxi)\npaste(rows